","msg":"依啲國際組織都係垃圾黎<br />\n上次聯合國出嗰份聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"又係失敗論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"你都on9 失你老母"},{"pid":"d5c9976f6e71aa7829084d239c2ff1dbcaa8e9e3","tid":1721213,"uid":59789,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033b380ce06ee6e62fb65784296de53750d23430","tid":1721213,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1806fa608f6a6d21d0cfea82defa8d24bbec25","tid":1721213,"uid":59789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"依啲國際組織都係垃圾黎<br />\n上次聯合國出嗰份聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"又係失敗論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔屌鳩你真係唔撚得<br />\n我話啲國際組織係垃圾就等於我話會失敗？<br />\n咪撚on9啦<br />\n死仆街分化撚<br />\n今次一定贏 失你老母閪個敗咩"},{"pid":"6c21516e575274cce9fcd9e904131b0719d96157","tid":1721213,"uid":111720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b014af6eba3b133ccd4cdee941f30556116267be","tid":1721213,"uid":177600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"推上去啦 救自己人"},{"pid":"ebb8a10d036960887e9d1ff87bf30ffadac0a87e","tid":1721213,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511ad1b068e2bd5790f975be45154bf028964348","tid":1721213,"uid":187799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0077592c3b737911606c265ac0cfb83808440d3","tid":1721213,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b0ffd0b73367dfa499d416cd906c8688848377","tid":1721213,"uid":330260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1baf36265c7db38045d0bf9844e4e0ca29e58289","tid":1721213,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22d78c9d4c3f52f605cee975d70e8c0a854c478d","tid":1721213,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"立場記者 陳裕匡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「氯痤瘡。最近有記者同前線開始岀。tg 有人講。終於看得到了。」<br />\n<br />\n五個月過去，醫生証實我長岀了氯痤瘡。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上資料，氯痤瘡是目前唯一可確認，人體積存高濃度二噁英的表徵。<br />\n<br />\n1976 年，意大利倫巴底地區有化工廠爆炸，高濃度二噁英外洩，二噁英覆蓋達 320 公頃，當地出現約 200 名氯痤瘡。越戰期間，美軍使用惡名昭彰的橙劑。對，即是令樹葉凋落、使叢林中的越共遊擊士兵現蹤影的落葉劑。三十多年過去，仍有不少退伍軍人被驗出體內積存過量的二噁英。患者有氯痤瘡與抑鬱病徵。<br />\n<br />\n幸而，氯痤瘡只是表徵，內裡會有甚麼問題或是有無問題，還要一段時間、一段經歴、一條命水去決定。可能沒事呢。不過也逆轉不能了。<br />\n<br />\n在毛記接受訪問，有條問答最後好像沒有岀街。我不太確定。被問到我或我的同事朋友被射盲眼或重傷，大約意思，我會怎麼辦。我説，我會繼續做下去，最少一段時間，最少不會因為身體而放棄。因為，那個傷，使我與我在觀察、在促成的事扣連著，逼我每天直視，不能抽身。對，我會繼續。<br />\n<br />\n可能一直到我老年都會沒事呢。不過也逆轉不能了吧。也換言之，我也會繼續做我在做的事，只要身邊的人不嫌棄，最少不會因傷棄陣。<br />\n<br />\n只要每天好好愛人、好好愛自己、做好要做的事、以自己最擅長的方法介入這個城市，就不枉此生。我會繼續加油、盡做。<br />\n<br />\n我愛你們。"},{"pid":"2b6632f872da52bb3c79b5cd39fdb8b1220bf0b9","tid":1721213,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ba0b3e4177d0aa3a91cfd2af76094de41677469","tid":1721213,"uid":203285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"一推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"世衛一早淪陷左係支共手上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街雞珍之前就係佢地傀儡<br />\n多次欺壓台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72276c7619e0deeff3e64b698977827d638553ef","tid":1721213,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b6632f872da52bb3c79b5cd39fdb8b1220bf0b9","tid":1721213,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ba0b3e4177d0aa3a91cfd2af76094de41677469","tid":1721213,"uid":203285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"一推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"世衛一早淪陷左係支共手上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街雞珍之前就係佢地傀儡<br />\n多次欺壓台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"可能仲幫埋中共隱瞞鼠疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔理啦, 照拉埋WHO落水先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0961ddba3cfb4496b5bda980eb82398597f11631","tid":1721213,"uid":138144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:20:34.000Z","msg":"Bump"},{"pid":"1f6a6c6e27022c8259cfe76c212470178f606130","tid":1721213,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"仲有死去既動物"},{"pid":"e552fbf146ff9d9b5709319f64db32a977c8c636","tid":1721213,"uid":52095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"7977ff287223d060d654968038ab05a399604adc","tid":1721213,"uid":221611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49cef950bade27cbf9e6884f3a323208f54951dc","tid":1721213,"uid":256791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4035a29c5cbd918f7ca5932144b007c9dad59479","tid":1721213,"uid":286589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4371ce76848654d21ab7015fc516b20e0af8f36","tid":1721213,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d258c9abc9cabbb65baa2152bf5a348d244f25","tid":1721213,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"撞<br />\n推"},{"pid":"5b986eaa290aee767d8d7fdf0890fa86da8f00a5","tid":1721213,"uid":21319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61379a38df22571630a74d6db1b0566128ce396b","tid":1721213,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68ccf8ccf4e0925adfe3ee69a3e071b47c1c096b","tid":1721213,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"警方日前強攻中大時，射出逾千枚催淚彈，現場囤積高濃度的催淚化合物（CS）。化學博士兼名師K.Kwong昨日（14日）在facebook連番出post，形容中大已淪為「大化學反應堆」，污染濃度很高，包括因高溫燃燒而從催淚化合物中分解出來的二噁英，已毒害附近的鳥和魚，呼籲留守者立即離開，保障健康。由於二噁英溶於脂肪又穩定，積存人體多年亦難以排清和分解，根治無期。<span style=\"color: red;\">K.Kwong更特別提到，現時防暴警的裝備無法阻擋二噁英，並會將其帶往警署及家中，可能損害警員及其家人的生殖能力，導致流產及畸胎。<br />\n</span><br />\n持續5個月的抗暴之戰中，防暴警在各區「催淚彈放題」，催淚化合物幾乎遍佈香港每個角落。K.Kwong再次在網上解釋催淚煙的禍害，指因高溫而由催淚化合物分解出來的二噁英污染物，難以清洗和抵擋，警告一般市民不要自行清洗。他更特別提到，防暴警現時身穿的裝備，並非「NBC Nato」型面罩，無法阻擋吸入二噁英；而二噁英亦會殘留於衣物與裝備上，令污染物帶至警署及家中，或影響前線警及其家人的精子及生殖能力，更有可能導致流產及畸胎。"},{"pid":"d8c519d7e1479a8c14776103dbc97aedfe5cdd8e","tid":1721213,"uid":51411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:10:06.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人可聯絡到任何呢方面專家<br />\n講真我地求世界關注之前 都應該提供啲實則理據<br />\n我好支持做測試化驗 <br />\nIf有人肯去帶頭 我相信錢 同埋sample應該不成問題"},{"pid":"2c8b071a07cd257133c63fafa8567359704133c7","tid":1721213,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8c519d7e1479a8c14776103dbc97aedfe5cdd8e","tid":1721213,"uid":51411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:10:06.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人可聯絡到任何呢方面專家<br />\n講真我地求世界關注之前 都應該提供啲實則理據<br />\n我好支持做測試化驗 <br />\nIf有人肯去帶頭 我相信錢 同埋sample應該不成問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:16:54.000Z","msg":"好似有人做緊測試，不過兩樣野應該無衝突的，民間一邊做，另一邊比壓力WHO要回應，可以並行"},{"pid":"5d8063fb3ca97f56886bcec322f59bcbc62d9431","tid":1721213,"uid":273090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:05:57.000Z","msg":"呢個重要！快啲做左佢！"},{"pid":"a8b6cd8888f7c25f595c255b79e0288b6c7a0e7e","tid":1721213,"uid":232509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f14a8f9948aac2a9e41d5a96ec55fe9673c62ca","tid":1721213,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:50:53.000Z","msg":"高汁post留名"},{"pid":"6cdb2ae2fd8e4341e10a4881bd2548b9dd6a6ab3","tid":1721213,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:11:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8161a82cb1b31df31112578d5dea212876a8fa7f","tid":1721213,"uid":240272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"推，有冇用都要做左先知"},{"pid":"3d0ec4fbe786eb2011608837beba41aea43b15a5","tid":1721213,"uid":143124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9e5649293a116c97bc6d52065a9b40a864dd2eb","tid":1721213,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb21d8b223608c63807f2